---
title: Double All-American Pork & Roast Pumpkin Slaw with Mayonnaise & Parsley
description: Tonight is a celebration in a bowl, so get your knives and forks at the ready because once this dish hits the table it’s party time. Let your taste buds dance away to the show stopping pumpkin dressed in a zesty slaw. The real fun begins when you take a bite of tender spiced pork, seared, sliced and drizzled in mayo.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
